<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbf19e7cf-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s10201"><num value="10201">§ 10201.</num><heading> Judicial review</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Judicial review of research and development activities under this subchapter shall be in accordance with the provisions of <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s10139">section 10139 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbf19e7d0-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/97/425/tII/s221">Pub. L. 97–425, title II, § 221</ref>, <date date="1983-01-07">Jan. 7, 1983</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/96/2254">96 Stat. 2254</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
